                <p xml:id="KR3b0003-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-07T05:02:34.054+09:00">“孙子说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-07T05:02:41.203+09:00">军事学研究</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-07T05:02:48.011+09:00">是国家的大事，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-1a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-07T05:02:54.283+09:00">它是关乎百姓死活、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-1a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-07T05:03:01.222+09:00">国家存亡的一个思想领域，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-1a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-07T15:28:48.375+09:00">不能不深入考察。”</seg>
                </p>
